{"tid":174382,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"點解老豆隻耳咁撚靈","createTime":"2017-03-26T17:54:30.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-28T18:54:54.000Z","uid":42197,"like":4,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"adb59df423e8dea539df959538d61e30bba8581a","tid":174382,"uid":42197,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-26T17:54:30.000Z","msg":"事源就係我阿媽瞓覺好大鼻鼾，搞到老豆頂唔順出廳瞓，但係平時聽野又唔見佢咁靈，一到夜晚要瞓覺聽到少少聲就鬧鳩我嘈住佢瞓。<br />\n啱啱沖涼，開咗個spotify聽歌，用4格聲量聽到去《經過一些秋與冬》已經俾啲水聲遮到我聽唔到咁濟，佢竟然喺到敲門，又熄鳩我燈話我嘈。出到嚟又屌我話我唔體諒佢，咁我同阿哥間房隔棟牆再加個天窗，佢啲鼻鼾扯到我瞓唔到又有邊個體諒我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唉總之我做乜都係錯啦屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n利申四人公屋"},{"pid":"baf60a7b8a67ee7bd3d5f66e1ca2e5439f044373","tid":174382,"uid":78039,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-26T17:55:37.000Z","msg":"因為佢登特出盡耳力去聽搵人屌"},{"pid":"fb6ce2f04fba29737ed72b2a4a3190eb0022d07f","tid":174382,"uid":89999,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-26T17:56:15.000Z","msg":"在那些爭拗中 我有心不夠用"},{"pid":"63edc23f4776add177425212e12f180e3b297bca","tid":174382,"uid":42197,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-26T17:56:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>因為佢登特出盡耳力去聽搵人屌</blockquote><br />\n佢又已經無返工，我真係諗唔到佢邊忽有壓力要搵人屌喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"71581479d96d37f2bbb392bef3edbb0746be34e5","tid":174382,"uid":43308,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-26T17:56:52.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"edf80b234ccc9a746a0551507c7ea90ed30cfe2f","tid":174382,"uid":42197,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-26T17:56:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>在那些爭拗中 我有心不夠用</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d857f3c7a530138f87baef9b0dfea49b4b276e10","tid":174382,"uid":43308,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-26T17:57:20.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"aa2d10358e39a45666efd268903eece85f4acbc4","tid":174382,"uid":93091,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-26T17:58:08.000Z","msg":"應該係情緒去到臨界點，你咁啱唔好彩<br />\n乖唔洗喊，你無錯"},{"pid":"57b92f979cd17c3e197a3b378f4c97771940dcd7","tid":174382,"uid":42197,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-26T17:59:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>因為佢登特出盡耳力去聽搵人屌</blockquote><br />\n佢又已經無返工，我真係諗唔到佢邊忽有壓力要搵人屌喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n就係無返工嘅人先會咁啊! 你唔明<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n無事搵野嚟嘈，講到自己好撚委屈咁。<br />\n仲有啊佢平時好撚中意開大個bass播埋啲大陸歌，又大大聲播陶傑播到十二點，又唔見佢諗下阿媽瞓唔瞓到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d6cc67fb3e370cce2eec242dfa3888f589d134ac","tid":174382,"uid":42197,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-26T18:01:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>應該係情緒去到臨界點，你咁啱唔好彩<br />\n乖唔洗喊，你無錯</blockquote><br />\n我哽咽啫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n佢晚晚都鬧我嘈架，樓下大聲嘈交嘈到有回音又唔見佢瞓唔到，我關埋房門傾電話就屌我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"30f3576371cf60df301fedf8741895d6c388d804","tid":174382,"uid":93091,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-26T18:03:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>因為佢登特出盡耳力去聽搵人屌</blockquote><br />\n佢又已經無返工，我真係諗唔到佢邊忽有壓力要搵人屌喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n就係無返工嘅人先會咁啊! 你唔明<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n無事搵野嚟嘈，講到自己好撚委屈咁。<br />\n仲有啊佢平時好撚中意開大個bass播埋啲大陸歌，又大大聲播陶傑播到十二點，又唔見佢諗下阿媽瞓唔瞓到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我老豆都係咁，成日覺得佢想用亂鬧人呢種方式去發曳<br />\n一有少少唔啱佢心水就出聲，跟住對其他兄弟特別好，淨係唔理我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"545e49b6686951d0f22fbb078ce21cd71e53ecc3","tid":174382,"uid":43308,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-26T18:03:52.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"290e87d1f7ba02abdabd3768e9aff0f8fc77f75a","tid":174382,"uid":93091,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-26T18:05:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>應該係情緒去到臨界點，你咁啱唔好彩<br />\n乖唔洗喊，你無錯</blockquote><br />\n我哽咽啫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n佢晚晚都鬧我嘈架，樓下大聲嘈交嘈到有回音又唔見佢瞓唔到，我關埋房門傾電話就屌我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n傻嘅，無事無事，我都經歷緊<br />\n唔好喊，我支持你<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8d526f7394070361b162908bd47466dd89e573c3","tid":174382,"uid":42197,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-26T18:06:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>因為佢登特出盡耳力去聽搵人屌</blockquote><br />\n佢又已經無返工，我真係諗唔到佢邊忽有壓力要搵人屌喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n就係無返工嘅人先會咁啊! 你唔明<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n無事搵野嚟嘈，講到自己好撚委屈咁。<br />\n仲有啊佢平時好撚中意開大個bass播埋啲大陸歌，又大大聲播陶傑播到十二點，又唔見佢諗下阿媽瞓唔瞓到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我老豆都係咁，成日覺得佢想用亂鬧人呢種方式去發曳<br />\n一有少少唔啱佢心水就出聲，跟住對其他兄弟特別好，淨係唔理我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n其實成家人都唔中意同佢相處，我已經係比較會關心佢果個（不過屋企本身係好含蓄，連對唔住都唔會講）<br />\n成日都想佢返大陸，因為佢一返就成個月先返嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f51385614497800c2c507f4942163f0455457f77","tid":174382,"uid":42197,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-26T18:06:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>努力設法逃離啦<br />\n<br />\n香港急需大量細單位 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n香港其實急需大量劏房<br />\n<br />\n大單位無撚用, 大而無當, 逼人發生爭執</blockquote><br />\n我十九歲咋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 劏房都租唔起啊"},{"pid":"d907c352a6c8af53d29ad0df4564cb671918e813","tid":174382,"uid":93091,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-26T18:09:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>因為佢登特出盡耳力去聽搵人屌</blockquote><br />\n佢又已經無返工，我真係諗唔到佢邊忽有壓力要搵人屌喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n就係無返工嘅人先會咁啊! 你唔明<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n無事搵野嚟嘈，講到自己好撚委屈咁。<br />\n仲有啊佢平時好撚中意開大個bass播埋啲大陸歌，又大大聲播陶傑播到十二點，又唔見佢諗下阿媽瞓唔瞓到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我老豆都係咁，成日覺得佢想用亂鬧人呢種方式去發曳<br />\n一有少少唔啱佢心水就出聲，跟住對其他兄弟特別好，淨係唔理我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n其實成家人都唔中意同佢相處，我已經係比較會關心佢果個（不過屋企本身係好含蓄，連對唔住都唔會講）<br />\n成日都想佢返大陸，因為佢一返就成個月先返嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n正，咪好似放監咁<br />\n叫班朋友上黎開party<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f5c967d66d0fd930727f3a90d75004091254cf2c","tid":174382,"uid":12782,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-26T18:09:55.000Z","msg":"脾氣好係被人蝦架啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c95c00fd942dc9f4d3b522d71daf677cf8ef29ad","tid":174382,"uid":15309,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-26T18:12:48.000Z","msg":"你每日定時定候對住個公仔喪鬧<br />\n鬧得興起果陣拎刀/棍打隻公仔<br />\n鬧10至20分鐘唔好停<br />\n過多排佢就唔敢嘈你"},{"pid":"75af6afb49ffb2f4d6021e097ea9cc549a289f8f","tid":174382,"uid":75440,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-26T18:13:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3e901a2e32348c75e66a2a855bfdbe34c27f9b06","tid":174382,"uid":62442,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-26T18:13:40.000Z","msg":"咁似我老豆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a6f7a8cd53c1f2547e20026059b0694d4989c5a1","tid":174382,"uid":33874,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-26T18:13:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>努力設法逃離啦<br />\n<br />\n香港急需大量細單位 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n香港其實急需大量劏房<br />\n<br />\n大單位無撚用, 大而無當, 逼人發生爭執</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n你知唔知乜撚係大單位？<br />\n真正大少少既單位，隔音好少少，根本乜問題都無"},{"pid":"bfa97766b97529221864fedaf41f90cf8b84c64d","tid":174382,"uid":42197,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-26T18:14:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>因為佢登特出盡耳力去聽搵人屌</blockquote><br />\n佢又已經無返工，我真係諗唔到佢邊忽有壓力要搵人屌喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n就係無返工嘅人先會咁啊! 你唔明<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n無事搵野嚟嘈，講到自己好撚委屈咁。<br />\n仲有啊佢平時好撚中意開大個bass播埋啲大陸歌，又大大聲播陶傑播到十二點，又唔見佢諗下阿媽瞓唔瞓到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我老豆都係咁，成日覺得佢想用亂鬧人呢種方式去發曳<br />\n一有少少唔啱佢心水就出聲，跟住對其他兄弟特別好，淨係唔理我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n其實成家人都唔中意同佢相處，我已經係比較會關心佢果個（不過屋企本身係好含蓄，連對唔住都唔會講）<br />\n成日都想佢返大陸，因為佢一返就成個月先返嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n正，咪好似放監咁<br />\n叫班朋友上黎開party<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n公屋邊敢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"83f1e0de0af8854e03c5aeeb6f245a4256d9967a","tid":174382,"uid":42197,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-26T18:16:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你每日定時定候對住個公仔喪鬧<br />\n鬧得興起果陣拎刀/棍打隻公仔<br />\n鬧10至20分鐘唔好停<br />\n過多排佢就唔敢嘈你</blockquote><br />\n佢都好喪架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 細個一曳就會俾佢打<br />\n試過小學果陣去咗個曳同學屋企玩，玩到八點先返屋企，結果俾佢用丫叉打到我對腳流血咁濟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"284e26795a4ed7647e17cc7fa86d81e9ddd37b89","tid":174382,"uid":77584,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-26T18:17:05.000Z","msg":"搵存在感<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n當佢單機番一兩個月就冇咁麻煩<br />\n平時同佢愈多交流就愈多野比佢挑骨頭"},{"pid":"e50d4afaf3cdd3c35397a273b02283ad2f9ed449","tid":174382,"uid":42197,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-26T18:17:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>咁似我老豆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n係咪啲老豆都係咁無聊搵野鬧<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"85fcf45a3ac4618304f7eed05940e435c7cef67b","tid":174382,"uid":340,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-26T18:18:22.000Z","msg":"成件事冇人錯，錯在窮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"26d645663856cb68e149619f6ae71bbb32bc6e64","tid":174382,"uid":43308,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-26T18:18:24.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"6fe838acc5ca32a2ef5e35247acb5d2d72fe4461","tid":174382,"uid":43308,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-26T18:18:44.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"eb4b5cf41e1eb504cb95f21868cb26a3f8aada7b","tid":174382,"uid":42197,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-26T18:18:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>搵存在感<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n當佢單機番一兩個月就冇咁麻煩<br />\n平時同佢愈多交流就愈多野比佢挑骨頭</blockquote><br />\n其實都唔算好多交流，一日最多傾幾句計，所以呢個我估唔係理由<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5d89f9368cfb7178e41e1f1a0dcb3f57774a2176","tid":174382,"uid":42197,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-26T18:20:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>成件事冇人錯，錯在窮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\ntrue<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 窮撚真係無資格生存"},{"pid":"ec2962edd8b1618a502aaaa597c6c88d37274e6c","tid":174382,"uid":84277,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-26T18:20:41.000Z","msg":"黎我度住<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"83d36de399a4875e163c581e02aca835ed56e047","tid":174382,"uid":82602,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-26T18:21:01.000Z","msg":"阻人訓教係咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 你諗下佢平時番工好撚攰想休息下果啲囉<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n成個我老豆咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 憎人嘈住佢訓 自己放假又嘈番我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c174d1fe4941fcabc3ec631ed250ca6429945ef5","tid":174382,"uid":93091,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-26T18:21:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>因為佢登特出盡耳力去聽搵人屌</blockquote><br />\n佢又已經無返工，我真係諗唔到佢邊忽有壓力要搵人屌喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n就係無返工嘅人先會咁啊! 你唔明<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n無事搵野嚟嘈，講到自己好撚委屈咁。<br />\n仲有啊佢平時好撚中意開大個bass播埋啲大陸歌，又大大聲播陶傑播到十二點，又唔見佢諗下阿媽瞓唔瞓到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我老豆都係咁，成日覺得佢想用亂鬧人呢種方式去發曳<br />\n一有少少唔啱佢心水就出聲，跟住對其他兄弟特別好，淨係唔理我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n其實成家人都唔中意同佢相處，我已經係比較會關心佢果個（不過屋企本身係好含蓄，連對唔住都唔會講）<br />\n成日都想佢返大陸，因為佢一返就成個月先返嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n正，咪好似放監咁<br />\n叫班朋友上黎開party<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n公屋邊敢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我都係，平時叫朋友上黎打牌都唔敢太大聲，住老人區<br />\n乖喇唔好喊，抹乾眼淚早啲瞓<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/lomore_kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"26aa68bb5254ecf4067a2747b1308eee319441e1","tid":174382,"uid":19505,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-26T18:21:36.000Z","msg":"水聲大過歌聲咪嘈囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f0a89f7bb0702ed0b677062e31d314a5d22bcdbe","tid":174382,"uid":42197,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-26T18:23:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>阻人訓教係咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 你諗下佢平時番工好撚攰想休息下果啲囉<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n成個我老豆咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 憎人嘈住佢訓 自己放假又嘈番我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n佢鬼有返工，日日一係去行山行博物館，一係留喺屋企開行bass聽歌聽電台"},{"pid":"641f1b81f94b54209c11a3f3094f37b64f66d354","tid":174382,"uid":42197,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-26T18:24:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>水聲大過歌聲咪嘈囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" 